description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'Whole Body Pilates' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Move through a foundational pilates structure with Christie from Achill Island in County Mayo. ...
